=== banana bread

- 3/4 cups flour
- 1t baking powder
- 1t salt
- 3T butter
- 1/3c sugar
- 1 egg
- 1 banana

350degF for 30-50m

=== fruit cake

- 1 stick (1/2c) butter
- 1c flour
- 1t baking powder
- 1t salt
- 1/2c sugar
- 2 eggs
- 1lb fruit (approx)

Beat butter and sugar, then add eggs, then dry ingredients.
350degF for like an hour.

=== pie crust

- 2.5c flour
- 2 sticks butter
- 1/2c cold water (approx)
- 1t salt
- 2t sugar (if sweet crust desired)

