=== caramel cake

Mix

- 4T cup brown sugar
- 1.25c ap flour
- 2t baking powder
- 7T butter, melted
- 1 egg
- 1/2c milk
- 4T syrup

and pour into pan. On top, spread

- 1/2c brown sugar
- 2T boiling water?

bake 40m at 350degF